    <panel_attributes>Outline
-
Dungeon Game - 100 floors
Boss fight every 10 floors
Visit shop and heal after every 10
-
The Game:
-
--&gt; Introduction to story/ set up
--&gt; Random event generated 3 times
		- Shop (vendor, dojo, wizardry)
		- Encounter
--&gt; Fight generated 7 times		
--&gt; Repeat until boss + heal
      - Bosses are not random
--&gt; Sequence for end of game
-
Combat System:
-
Player stats: 
- Energy (100) and mana (30)
- Attack, Defense, and HP
- Gold for shop
Actual fights (boss and normal):
--&gt; Note: attacks have a formula
--&gt; Player chooses from three options
        - Physical attack (energy)
        - Spells (mana)
        - Guard (restores energy/reduces damage)
--&gt; Enemy goes and chooses random action
} Above sequence repeats until one loses
 - Player collects gold
 - Also replenishes 1/5 max energy
-</panel_attributes>
