    <panel_attributes>Encounters
-
Healing Fountain:
--&gt; Restores HP and Energy by 50%

Mysterious Rock:
--&gt; Given an option to dig the rock...
--&gt; Two outcomes random
- Gain gold from rock and continue
- OR Fight a Rockalyte

Warlock:
--&gt; You can choose to trade HP 
       for mana at a Gold cost
--&gt; Encounter ends after you've
       done a trade once or declined

Duelist:
--&gt; You can choose to fight a 
       powerful duelist or reject
--&gt; Gain lots of Gold if you win

Rock Slide:
--&gt; Hurts you for a certain amount
       of HP

Dart Trap:
--&gt; Player is warned of a dart trap,
       they are given a window of time
       to quickly react
--&gt; They escape if they react in time
       ,otherwise they take damage

Card Shark:
--&gt; Player can pay to take part in
        blackjack
--&gt; Gain double gold back if they
        win
--&gt; Can happen until player cancels

Dryad:
--&gt; Player can pay large sum of gold
       to restore all stats to full

